          How to obtain a hard copy of this Report
          (In stock as of 3/19/2001)

             The Data Dissemination Branch of the National Center on Health
             Statistics is handling the public distribution of this report.

             They can be reached by calling (301) 458-4636 or by emailing
             nchsquery@cdc.gov.
